## Agentic SOC Kali host telemetry rule set
## Captures user-space execve activity so the host-side audit bridge can classify suspicious commands.

-a always,exit -F arch=b64 -S execve -F auid>=1000 -F auid!=unset -k agentic_exec
-a always,exit -F arch=b32 -S execve -F auid>=1000 -F auid!=unset -k agentic_exec
